# Claude Cache .gitignore Template
#
# Add these lines to your main .gitignore file if you want to keep
# the cache out of version control
#
# Benefits of ignoring:
# - Keeps repo clean
# - Cache is regenerated as needed
# - Prevents cache conflicts between devs
#
# Benefits of committing:
# - Faster onboarding for new devs
# - Cache available in deployed environments
# - Team shares same context
#
# Recommendation: Ignore it (regenerate as needed)

# Claude cache folder
.claude_cache/

# Or keep overview but ignore sessions
.claude_cache/sessions/
